{"tid":529884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我一定唔會忘記廢佬哥基空降新西最後比何君堯入左","createTime":"2018-01-15T08:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T08:36:13.000Z","uid":48,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"66c62326b2d83ee298110877d0a720f72376db94","tid":529884,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T08:18:03.000Z","msg":"2016立法會 條廢佬空降新西<br />\n<br />\n跟住同李卓人 黃浩銘攬炒<br />\n<br />\n每人拎住萬幾票 最後一席比何老妖漁人得利<br />\n<br />\n你條死廢佬 今日終於現眼報 過主啦仆街"},{"pid":"8c77e8b0ab955f49ca45c8a2a5eed614e38ada41","tid":529884,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T08:22:55.000Z","msg":"我都唔會忘記<br />\n好地地選番佢個九西咪算囉<br />\n<br />\n又唔係唔知新西抵抗保皇狗頂得幾辛苦"},{"pid":"50017719d4669bedd906f660824f5ffda3944bd6","tid":529884,"uid":101396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"哥基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5ae69d24e017937a554efc67586a659455aec1","tid":529884,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c77e8b0ab955f49ca45c8a2a5eed614e38ada41","tid":529884,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T08:22:55.000Z","msg":"我都唔會忘記<br />\n好地地選番佢個九西咪算囉<br />\n<br />\n又唔係唔知新西抵抗保皇狗頂得幾辛苦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T08:36:13.000Z","msg":"因為再上一屆佢轉戰超級區議會九西個位俾咗黨友出戰<br />\n點知上屆個區議會席位俾獻世派搶咗<br />\n咁佢又唔信得失黨友返九西選<br />\n就去咗新西想搶人議席"}]}